==不雅裸露法律==
根据[[美国|美国]]关于裸体和公众礼仪法律，[[纽约州|纽约州]]、[[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]]、[[缅因州|缅因州]]、[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]]和[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]明确允许男性和女性在公共场合裸露上身。但是，大部分[[美国州份|美国州份]]或者明确或者不明确的认为女性裸露乳晕有伤风化，是一种犯罪行为。[[亚利桑那州|亚利桑那州]]、[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]、[[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]]、[[伊利诺伊州|伊利诺伊州]]、[[纽约州|纽约州]]、[[南卡罗来纳州|南卡罗来纳州]]、[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]和[[华盛顿州|华盛顿州]]的法律明确区分了[[母乳餵養|餵哺母乳]]和公共场合猥亵的不同。<ref>HG.org. [http://www.hg.org/article.asp?id=31193 "Nudity and Public Decency Laws in America"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hg.org/article.asp?id=31193 |date=20210116042536 }}. ''HG.org''. Retrieved on 20 January 2015.</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://udn.com/news/story/7546/817513-%E7%94%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5-%E5%A5%B3%E4%BA%BA%E4%B9%9F%E8%A1%8C%EF%BC%81%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E3%80%8C%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E4%B9%B3%E9%A0%AD%E3%80%8D | title=男人可以 女人也行！全球女性「解放乳頭」 | work=聯合新聞網 | date=2015-04-05 | accessdate=2015-04-23 | archive-date=2015-05-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150511223336/http://udn.com/news/story/7546/817513-%E7%94%B7%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5-%E5%A5%B3%E4%BA%BA%E4%B9%9F%E8%A1%8C%EF%BC%81%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E3%80%8C%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E4%B9%B3%E9%A0%AD%E3%80%8D | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在[[英国|英国]]，裸露上身不是一种违法行为。2009年[[伦敦警察厅|伦敦警察厅]]向[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]表示“在公共场合裸体不是犯罪”。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/magazine/8235959.stm |title=BBC NEWS {{!}} UK {{!}} Magazine {{!}} When does public nakedness become a crime?<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2015-07-28 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109033204/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/magazine/8235959.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>在[[英国|英国]]，在任何沙滩上裸晒都是合法的，而且裸体骑行活动每年都在举办。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/article/33092812/this-is-where-you-can-be-naked-in-public-in-the-uk |title=This is where you can be naked in public in the UK - BBC Newsbeat<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2015-07-28 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124002354/http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/article/33092812/this-is-where-you-can-be-naked-in-public-in-the-uk |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://guavanthropology.tw/article/6433|title=妳／你的乳頭解放了沒？ - 新一波性／別平權與身體情慾除罪化運動|date=2015-04-27|newspaper=guavanthropology.tw 芭樂人類學|accessdate=2017-03-03|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228102451/https://guavanthropology.tw/article/6433|dead-url=no}}</ref>但是，Stephen Gough已经由于违反了限制其在公共场合裸体的限制令而在[[苏格兰|苏格兰]]的监狱服刑多年。在[[美国|美国]][[俄勒冈州|俄勒冈州]][[尤金市|尤金市]]，在市中心裸露上身是完全合法的。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://queerology.net/2015/04/hot-spring-and-naked-in-public/|title=【客座】裸湯、混浴、自己的身體自己露 – Queerology|accessdate=2017-03-03|work=queerology.net|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929161215/http://queerology.net/2015/04/hot-spring-and-naked-in-public/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==网络审查==
作为对于[[美国文化|美国文化]]的一种表现，网络文化也一直将女性乳头作为一种禁忌，很多社交媒体，比如[[脸书|脸书]]和[[Instagram|Instagram]]禁止任何含有女性乳晕的图片内容。<ref name="Facebook War on Nipples">Esco, Lina. [http://www.huffingtonpost.com/lina-esco/facebook-war-on-nipples_b_4548832.html "Facebook Wages War on the Nipple"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/lina-esco/facebook-war-on-nipples_b_4548832.html |date=20170830015617 }} ''[[Huffington_Post|Huffington Post]]'', New York, 7 January 2014. Retrieved on 20 January 2015.</ref>[[Instagram|Instagram]]的社区守则要求其用户“穿上衣服”。但是这项规定貌似只被运用在了含有女性乳头的图片上，因为除非在乳晕被遮盖的情况下，这些图片会被[[Instagram|Instagram]]删除。与之形成对比的是，裸露上身的男性照片并不受此规定的约束。Chelsea Handler<ref>Marcotte, Amanda. [http://www.slate.com/blogs/xx_factor/2014/10/31/chelsea_handler_puts_a_topless_photo_on_instagram_and_protests_when_it_s.html "Chelsea Handler Stands Up for Freed Nipples"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.slate.com/blogs/xx_factor/2014/10/31/chelsea_handler_puts_a_topless_photo_on_instagram_and_protests_when_it_s.html |date=20180914223422 }}. ''[The Slate Group]'', 31 October 2014. Retrieved on 20 January 2015.</ref>， Miley Cyrus<ref>Hathaway, Jay. [http://gawker.com/miley-cyrus-frees-her-nipples-in-topless-instagram-phot-1675985556 "Miley Cyrus Frees Her Nipples in Topless Instagram Photo"] {{Wayback|url=http://gawker.com/miley-cyrus-frees-her-nipples-in-topless-instagram-phot-1675985556 |date=20150306065619 }}. ''[Gawker]'', New York, 29 December 2014. Retrieved on 2 March 2015.</ref>、Rihanna和Scout Willis<ref>Rosenfield, Kat. [http://www.mtv.com/news/1833899/scout-willis-topless-instagram-rihanna/ "Rihanna Joins Scout Willis In #FreeTheNipple Topless Instagram Campaign"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1833899/scout-willis-topless-instagram-rihanna/ |date=20201130072410 }}. ''[MTV]'', New York, 29 May 2014. Retrieved on 2 March 2015.</ref>都由于上传了裸露上身的照片而受到了批评。由于其身着的T恤上印有女性乳头，Willow Smith的一张照片也被删除，尽管那件衣服本身并没有什么不合适。<ref>Bacardi, Francesca. [http://www.eonline.com/news/617389/willow-smith-s-topless-picture-is-the-latest-instagram-naked-photo-controversy "Willow Smith's "Topless" Picture Is the Latest Instagram Naked Photo Controversy"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/617389/willow-smith-s-topless-picture-is-the-latest-instagram-naked-photo-controversy |date=20201028154638 }}. ''[E! Online]'', California, 22 January 2015. Retrieved on 2 March 2015.</ref>

==影片==

